criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — defined the goal and stakeholders to balance ("determine whether it creates value relative to alternative uses of cash while balancing stakeholder incentives"); 
Implement/Represent — laid out stakeholder-specific pros/cons and effects for each option (retail, institutional, management, bondholders; EPS, leverage, taxes); 
Reflect — weighed trade-offs, recommended buyback while acknowledging risks and suggesting mixed approaches.
